snippet.title: Slaughter League Open Alpha Test Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign up for you test key here: 

https://www.freedom.gg/slplaytest

Slaughter League is a fast-paced multiplayer extravaganza that will pit you against up to 10 friends (or enemies) in a daring race to the finish line. Run as fast as you can and watch out for those Tesla coils, jump as high as possible avoiding the buzzsaws, and slide your way to victory while dodging more spikes along the way!

Sign up for a key to gain access to the demo during our playtest windows and join in on the action!

April 2nd - Public Demo from Noon to 8pm Pacific Time (3pm to 11pm Eastern Time)

April 3rd - Public Demo from 9am to 6pm Pacific Time (1pm to 9pm Eastern Time)
